</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="202.[151,1436,1544,2037]" pageId="202" pageNumber="203">
Anchoring triactines (
<figureCitation box="[448,553,1544,1569]" captionStart="FIGURE 129" captionStartId="203.[151,250,1751,1773]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,519,1729]" captionTargetId="figure@203.[151,1436,519,1729]" captionTargetPageId="203" captionText="FIGURE 129. Amphoriscus ancora sp. nov., a – e, SEM images of the spicules of holotype RMNH Por. 9741, a, large cortical tetractines, b, small atrial tetractines, c, triactines, d, anchoring triactines, d 1, detail of d, e, root diactine, e 1, details of e." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/273079/files/figure.png" pageId="202" pageNumber="203">Figs 129</figureCitation>
d,d1) from the roots, with characteristically curved unpaired actine and beaklike paired actines, in a large size range, unpaired actines 96– 
<emphasis box="[833,875,1580,1605]" italics="true" pageId="202" pageNumber="203">386</emphasis>
–660 
<date box="[938,971,1581,1604]" pageId="202" pageNumber="203">x 7</date>
– 
<emphasis box="[986,1021,1580,1605]" italics="true" pageId="202" pageNumber="203">8.6</emphasis>
–10 µm, paired actines 18– 
<emphasis box="[1324,1373,1581,1605]" italics="true" pageId="202" pageNumber="203">24.8</emphasis>
– 
<date pageId="202" pageNumber="203" value="1929-10-05">29 x 5</date>
–6.8–9 µm.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="202.[151,1436,1544,2037]" box="[199,1189,1652,1677]" pageId="202" pageNumber="203">
Diactines (
<figureCitation box="[320,422,1652,1677]" captionStart="FIGURE 129" captionStartId="203.[151,250,1751,1773]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,519,1729]" captionTargetId="figure@203.[151,1436,519,1729]" captionTargetPageId="203" captionText="FIGURE 129. Amphoriscus ancora sp. nov., a – e, SEM images of the spicules of holotype RMNH Por. 9741, a, large cortical tetractines, b, small atrial tetractines, c, triactines, d, anchoring triactines, d 1, detail of d, e, root diactine, e 1, details of e." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/273079/files/figure.png" pageId="202" pageNumber="203">Figs 129</figureCitation>
e,e1) from the roots, long and thin, 600–1 
<emphasis box="[884,927,1653,1677]" italics="true" pageId="202" pageNumber="203">0 17</emphasis>
– 
<date box="[941,1037,1653,1677]" pageId="202" pageNumber="203" value="1230-10-03">1230 x 3</date>
